possibilites.}) ({the logical} 13... Be6 $143 {is weak too. After} 14. O-O-O c6
15. Bd3 h6 16. Ne4 $40 {white keeps great attacking prospects.}) ({one of the
two major moves in the position is} 13... Nxc3 $1 14. Bxc3 {and now the very
concrete} Qd5 {[%csl Rf3][%cal Gc8f5] with the idea of ...Qxf3 and ...Bf5.
Here I recommend going for} ({something like} 14... Be6 {is much weaker and
