[%cal Gh1d1,Ye4h7] where we keep some pressure.}) 14. Bd3 $1 (14. O-O-O $6 Nb4
$1 15. axb4 axb4 16. Nb1 Qf6 $17 {[%csl Rc1,Rf3][%cal Ge8e6,Ye6c6]}) 14... h6 {
the strongest choice for black.} (14... g6 {allows us to display our idea with
