16. e4 Nxc3 17. Bxc3 $16 {[%csl Rc7][%cal Gc3g7,Ge1c1,Yh5h6,Gc2c7] where
black's king is coming under huge pressure.}) 16. Bb5 $1 $146 {[%cal Gh5g6]
