useful for pushing e4.} Qd7 (14... Ne7 15. Rac1 c6 16. Na4 $14 {[%csl Rb6,Rc5]
[%cal Ga4c5,Gf3e5,Gb2b4]}) 15. e4 $1 dxe4 16. Nxe4 Nxe4 17. Bxe4 $14 {[%csl
Rc6][%cal Gd2c3]}) 13. g4 $5 $146 {a very ambitious response. We begin our
adventure with the threat of g5!} (13. O-O Qc8 $11) 13... b5 $1 {the strongest
response. Black looks to counterattack.} (13... Bd6 14. Rg1 b5 {Black's idea
is to meet} 15. g5 {with} hxg5 16. Rxg5 {[%cal Gc3d5]} Bf4 $3 {[%cal Rd7h3]
but here we have the surprising} 17. Rxd5 $1 {which helps us in maintaining
the initiative. After} Nxd5 18. Nxd5 Bh6 19. Ke2 $44 {[%csl Gc2,Rc6,Rc7,Gd3,
Gd5][%cal Ga1g1] White's position is easier to play}) 14. g5 hxg5 ({also
possible and complicated is} 14... b4 {with the point that after} 15. gxf6 Qxf6
{both the knight are hanging. We are forced to play} 16. Ne5 {where we
initiate a forced sequence} bxc3 (16... Nxe5 17. dxe5 Qf3 18. Rh2 bxc3 {
transposes.}) 17. Bxc3 Nxe5 18. dxe5 Qf3 (18... Qh4 {is slightly weaker
practically. After} 19. Bh7+ Kh8 20. Bf5 $1 Be6 21. O-O-O c5 22. Bxe6 fxe6 23.
Rdg1 {[%csl Rg7][%cal Gg1g4] white keeps some pressure}) 19. Rh2 {and now
black needs to play the subtle} Bxh3 $1 {which is easy to overlook. However,
the position is far from dead and we can continue with} 20. Rd1 {[%cal Gd1d5,
Gd3e2] threatening Be2-Rd5.} Bg4 $1 (20... Red8 $6 21. Bh7+ Kh8 22. Rd4 {
[%cal Gd4f4] we are exerting a lot of pressure here.}) (20... Qg4 {runs into
the very strong} 21. Kd2 Rad8 22. Kc1 {where we castle artificially. Black is
under pressure.}) 21. Rd2 c6 22. Bh7+ Kh8 23. Rd4 {and again black has to be
very precise to hold. These lines are quiet to play if you are unprepared.})
15. Rg1 $1 {introducing the rook into the attack.} b4 $1 (15... g4 16. hxg4
Bxg4 (16... b4 17. Nxd5 $18) 17. Ng5 Bd6 {[%cal Rc6d4]} 18. Kf1 $1 {[%csl Rf7]
[%cal Gc3d5,Gd3h7,Gg1g4] We keep great attacking chances here.}) 16. Nxg5 {
with a huge attack.} Bd6 $1 {[%cal Gc6d4,Yg8f8,Rd3h7]} (16... bxc3 $4 17. Bh7+
$18) 17. Nxd5 Nxd4 18. Qc4 $40 {[%cal Gd3g6,Yc4d4] with insane complications
but which are harder to black to navigate. We have all kinds of threats in the
air.} *

